Date: Wed, 27 Aug 2025 23:14:03 +0200
Subject: Upgrade PCRE2 to 10.46
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

New upstream release.

It fixes CVE-2025-58050, which is exploitable only on patterns
controlled by an attacker, which we don't support (patterns are security
sensitive as one may DOS an application). Still, apply the upgrade.

[ChangeLog][Third-Party Code] PCRE2 was updated to version 10.46.

Pick-to: 6.8 6.5
Change-Id: Ia52e73b9eb1f777eb02257406c30af26ed744509
